*********************************************
***********  xfce4-netspeed-plugin  **********
*********************************************

xfce4-netspeed-plugin shows the instant download / upload speed in the Xfce Panel.

** Requirements **

* libxfce4util 4.3.90
* libxfcegui4 4.3.90
* libxfce4panel 4.3.90			      
* libgtop 2.0

** Building **

./configure
make
make install (as root)

** Usage **

After properly installing it, you should find this plugin in the "Add New Items..." Xfce Panel dialog,
under the name "Network Speed Plugin". You can then tweak the plugin using the configuration dialog.
